quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"lbut ko Shasa-asa-ap sa Samporna a kasha-ap,"
  37,2,"Go so Puphamapundug (ko Gabon) sa Samporna a Kapanun­dug,"
  37,3,"Go so Puphamamatiya sa Pananadum (a manga Malaikat)!"
  37,4,"Mata-an! A so Tohan niyo na Matatangkud a Isa!-"
  37,5,"Kadnan o manga Langit a go so Lopa, go so paglutan a dowa oto, go Kadnan o manga Subangan!"
  37,6,"Mata-an! A Sukami na iniPharas Ami ko Langit a marani so Parahiyasan a manga Bito-on,-"
  37,7,"Go Siyap ko oman i Shaitan a gi-i mbinasa,"
  37,8,"Di ran maphamamakinug so (manga Malaikat a) a pagtao a Ma­ poro, ka Puphululubadun siran ko mbalabala,"
  37,9,"Sa kapamogao, go adun a bagiyan niran a siksa a Tatap,"
  37,10,"Inonta so miyakasinggaot sa isa a kasinggaot (ko Katharo o manga Malaikat), na siyaloba suka­ niyan o Sindao o Bito-on a Masin­dao (a Phakatotong)."
  37,11,"Na Paki-osain Ka kiran: o ba siran i lubi a Mabagur a Ka­ adun, antawa-a so Inadun Ami (i lubi a Mabagur)? Mata-an! A Suka­ mi na Inadun Ami siran a pho-on ko Lipao, a Mapilit!"
  37,12,"Kuna, ka Miyamumusa Ka, go Puphamagurugangka iran,"
  37,13,"Na igira a Piyakatadum sir­an, na di siran Phakatadum,-"
  37,14,"Go igira a Miyakailai siran sa tanda, na Puphamagurugan nir­an,"
  37,15,"Go Pitharo iran: A da ko ungkai inonta na Balik Mata a Ma­payag!"
  37,16,"Ino amai ka Matai kami, go mbaloi kami a botha, go manga tolan, ba Mata-an! A sukami na Pagoyagun kami dun?"
  37,17,"Antawa-a so manga Lokus ami a miyanga-o ona?"
  37,18,"Tharowangka: A owai, (Pa­goyagun kano dun), go sukano na Phamakarondan."
  37,19,"Na giyoto na satimambo a Lalis; na sa maoto na siran na ma­ kananayao siran!"
  37,20,"Go Matharo iran: A Hai dowan dowan tano! Giya i so Alon­gan a Kapamalas!"
  37,21,"(Na Tharo-on kiran:) Giya i so Alongan a Kokoman, a so suka­ no na Piyakambokhag iyo sukani­yan!"
  37,22,"(Tham-on o Allah ko manga Malaikat:) Limoda niyo so Mind­ adarowaka, rakhus o manga ogana­pa iran, go so Piyamanimba iran-"
  37,23,"A salakao ko Allah, na nggonanaowa niyo siran ko lalan ko Naraka Jahim!"
  37,24,"Go tarongkowa niyo siran, ka Mata-an! A siran na Pagisha-an siran:"